---
title: 'Chopped Cheese' Quesadillas with Potato Wedges and Honey-Garlic Dijonnaise
description: Tonight's dinner is a fun and flavourful twist on a classic Harlem bodega sandwich known as a 'chopped cheese.' Savoury ground beef is topped with sharp cheddar and juicy tomatoes before getting tucked into a tortilla shell. It's served with potato wedges and a honey-garlic Dijonnaise sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quesadillas-au-fromage-facon-bodegas-dharlem-4ef73d67.jpg
